quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  94,1,Have We not expanded your breast for you
  94,2,And laid aside from you your encumbrance
  94,3,Which weighed down your back
  94,4,And did We not raise for you your remembrance
  94,5,So surely with difficulty comes ease
  94,6,Surely with difficulty comes ease
  94,7,"So when you are at leisure, (i.e., not o) then labor"
  94,8,"And to your Lord then be desirous (i.e., of His Grace)"